                        +PAGE_LIKE_LIST_ITEM("02-make-time-for-personal-learning")
                      p
                        | Failing to make time for personal learning is like planning to fail. Make learning
                        | a priority by making a regular time commitment for it so that it becomes a routine habit. 
                  tr
                    td
                      h2
                        .tip-number
                          | #03
                        |  
                        a(href="personal/03-hide-away-change-the-scenery.html", title="Hide Away / Change The Scenery")
                          | Hide Away / Change The Scenery
                        +PAGE_LIKE_LIST_ITEM("03-hide-away-change-the-scenery")
                      p
                        | Find a place to learn that suits you - even if it means hiding away from your colleagues!
                  tr
                    td
                      h2
                        .tip-number
                          | #04
                        |  
                        a(href="personal/04-avoid-distractions-and-occasional-interruptions.html", title="Avoid Distractions And Occasional Interruptions")
                          | Avoid Distractions And Occasional Interruptions
                        +PAGE_LIKE_LIST_ITEM("04-avoid-distractions-and-occasional-interruptions")
                      p
                        | Discover the secret weapon enabling you to hide in plain sight to avoid distractions and
                        | occasional interruptions to maximise your learning time and productivity.
                  tr
                    td
                      h2
                        .tip-number
                          | #05
                        |  
                        a(href="personal/05-create-a-personal-development-plan.html", title="Create A Personal Development Plan")
                          | Create A Personal Development Plan
                        +PAGE_LIKE_LIST_ITEM("05-create-a-personal-development-plan")
                      p
                        | Having a personal development plan will help you plan and progress your personal learning journey
                        | helping you to turn good intentions into achievements.
                  tr
                    td
                      h2
                        .tip-number
                          | #06
                        |  
                        a(href="personal/06-learn-to-manage-your-time-well.html", title="Learn To Manage Your Time Well")
                          | Learn To Manage Your Time Well
                        +PAGE_LIKE_LIST_ITEM("06-learn-to-manage-your-time-well")
