                  tr
                    td
                      h2
                        .tip-number
                          | #07
                        |  
                        a(href="personal/07-find-ways-of-learning-that-work-for-you.html", title="Find Ways Of Learning That Work For You")
                          | Find Ways Of Learning That Work For You
                        +PAGE_LIKE_LIST_ITEM("07-find-ways-of-learning-that-work-for-you")
                      p
                        | Identifying your preferences for learning can make a huge difference to the effectiveness
                        | with which you learn. It is therefore important to take time to identify the ways of learning
                        | that work best for you.
                  tr
                    td
                      h2
                        .tip-number
                          | #08
                        |  
                        a(href="personal/08-join-a-community.html", title="Join A Community")
                          | Join A Community
                        +PAGE_LIKE_LIST_ITEM("08-join-a-community")
                      p
                        | Exploit the benefits of joining a community to broaden your horizons and learn from others.

              h2 Notifications

              p
